{
  "stem": "3933.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Later, they are going to confiscate again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They were afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Their landlord told them to move out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This is-- I jump from things to thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And they left, this couple.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The Jewish elderly couple left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They will find something, because they ask him to-- asked them to leave.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I took [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Erik-- ?] I took my son-- I called him [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Erik ?] now.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I'll never forget this thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I don't know where to go and what to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "My-- my-- my brother-in-law, the non-Jewish, wasn't even at home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He was lately-- he want to get rid of this obligation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] wife.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And the other-- and the child of another sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] and his wife.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They were his-- his responsibility.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Then I'll never forget, I walked out of the house, and I went into a toilet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And this toilet was so primitive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It's not like water-- it's not like-- you know, a different toilet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "What I mean-- I don't know-- you people ever read about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "This is something very primitive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "It's never flushed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "There is no construction.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "There is not a flush-- nothing to flush.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "This is the way it was in this place where I came from, even before the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "I know Americans couldn't imagine things like that-- the poor people, because this construction-- these things cost a lot-- the instruction in-- in-- to put things and all the-- the work-- is only for the wealthy one.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I stayed there with my son.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were until here and-- excuse my expression-- in-- in human stew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I say, where am I going to go?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where am I going to go?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I went to Mr.-- What is his name?",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
